    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/ThreeActions.webp",
      "name": "Ride Corpse",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The manananggal inserts their entrails into their humanoid body, allowing them to appear as and move about like a normal human. The body has 10 Hit Points and the same defenses as the manananggal. When the body is destroyed, the manananggal is ejected unharmed. The body becomes a corpse, and if it is neither controlled by the manananggal nor stored in an alchemical vat, it decays as normal.</p>"
        },
